    <briefdescription>
<para>Propagates activation state from parent to child entities. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system processes entities with HierarchyComponent and propagates their active/inactive state to all descendants. Only root entities (those without a parent) that are marked dirty trigger propagation.</para>
<para>The system runs in two passes:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Active roots: propagate active state to children</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Inactive roots: propagate inactive state to children </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
